OL,3,CBrittany Ferries to cut routes and
OL,4,Csell ships amid financial pressures
OL,6,FBrittany Ferries will sell two ships
OL,7,Fand cut some routes as the company
OL,8,Fsays it is adapting to "a new reality".
OL,10,FIn a statement, the French operator
OL,11,Fexplains the moves are necessary to
OL,12,Fease financial pressures "in the face
OL,13,Fof a rising tax burden, Covid loan
OL,14,Frepayments, cost-of-living concerns
OL,15,Famong passengers and unfair
OL,16,Fcompetition on the Eastern Channel".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/7
