PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1783693093
OL,3,CBrittany Ferries to cut routes and
OL,4,Csell ships amid financial pressures
OL,6,FThe ferry firm adds that half of its
OL,7,FCovid loan still needs to be paid
OL,8,Fback, alongside a separate #23 million
OL,9,Fbill from the EU, which forces
OL,10,Fpolluters to buy emission allowances
OL,11,Fonce they pass a certain cap.
OL,13,FAs well as offloading two ships, the
OL,14,FBarfleur and the Cotentin, Brittany
OL,15,FFerries will end its Portsmouth to Le
OL,16,FHavre and Poole to Cherbourg sailings
OL,17,Flater this year.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/7
