OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1783693093
OL,3,CBrittany Ferries to cut routes and
OL,4,Csell ships amid financial pressures
OL,6,FFrom 1 November, the Islander ferry
OL,7,Fwill serve a triangular route from
OL,8,FPortsmouth to Guernsey, Guernsey to
OL,9,FCherbourg, and Cherbourg to Portsmouth.
OL,11,FIt means there will no longer be a
OL,12,Fdirect route from the island to
OL,13,FPortsmouth, although the faster
OL,14,FVoyager ship will continue to serve
OL,15,Fthe Guernsey-Poole route.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
