CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1783693093
OL,3,CBrittany Ferries to cut routes and
OL,4,Csell ships amid financial pressures
OL,6,FBrittany Ferries explained: "Difficult
OL,7,Fdecisions are necessary to manage the
OL,8,Ffuture. A project has been initiated
OL,9,Fto allocate resources more
OL,10,Fefficiently, including consolidating
OL,11,Fservices where necessary and operating
OL,12,Fwith a cleaner and more efficient
OL,13,Ffleet."
OL,15,FElsewhere, the Commodore Clipper ferry
OL,16,Fwill be deployed to a new route,
OL,17,Fserving Cherbourg and Rosslare.
OL,19,FAccording to the States of Guernsey,
OL,20,Fit will remain their back-up vessel in
OL,21,Fcase of disruption.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1783693093
OL,3,CBrittany Ferries to cut routes and
OL,4,Csell ships amid financial pressures
OL,6,FDeputy Sasha Kazantseva-Miller,
OL,7,FPresident of the island's Economic
OL,8,FDevelopment Committee, said in a
OL,9,Fstatement that the group "are engaging
OL,10,Fwith key stakeholders to ensure that
OL,11,Fall operational, commercial and
OL,12,Fcommunity considerations are fully
OL,13,Funderstood before any final decision
OL,14,Fis made".
OL,16,FNeither of the ferries being sold are
OL,17,Fused on Guernsey sailings and the
OL,18,FDeputy told ITV News that there has
OL,19,Fbeen "very close collaboration"
OL,20,Fbetween the Government and the company.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1783693093
OL,3,CBrittany Ferries to cut routes and
OL,4,Csell ships amid financial pressures
OL,6,FThe States also stressed that the new
OL,7,Frotation would "preserve the existing
OL,8,F4am arrival time into Guernsey from
OL,9,FPortsmouth", as well as praising the
OL,10,Fnew direct sailings to Cherbourg.
OL,12,FWhen asked whether the changes would
OL,13,Fhave any effect on Guernsey Post, its
OL,14,FCEO Steve Sheridan said that "our
OL,15,Fexisting connectivity into the Royal
OL,16,FMail UK network remains unchanged".
OL,18,FHe added that they would continue to
OL,19,Fengage with Brittany Ferries in future
OL,20,Fdiscussions.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
