PN,35507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1783693093
OL,3,CBrittany Ferries to cut routes and
OL,4,Csell ships amid financial pressures
OL,6,FMeanwhile, the ferry company's CEO
OL,7,FChristophe Mathieu said the firm "need
OL,8,Fto adapt and that means a plan to
OL,9,Fsecure a future that will continue to
OL,10,Fbring opportunities for all those who
OL,11,Flive and work in the regions we serve".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/7
